	(gdk_pixbuf__ras_image_load): Updated invocation.
	(gdk_pixbuf__ras_image_begin_load): Add prefix.
	(gdk_pixbuf__ras_image_stop_load): Add prefix.
	(gdk_pixbuf__ras_image_load_increment): Add prefix.

